      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how heavy that feeling of constant noise has become for you, and it is valid to wish for a moment of true silence. Please remember that taking a step away from that pressure doesn't mean you are failing; it is simply a necessary act of survival to protect your well-being. You do not have to solve everything today, and it is okay to say no to the world for as long as it takes to find that stillness again.",
